description: Dept. of Elections - Elected Mr. Thalagawaththe Don Jayathissa and Mr. Apanayake Nimal Piyatissa of United People's Freedom Alliance as Members of Central Provincial Council - Elected Mr. Iyoob Asmin and Ms. Marykmala of Northern Provincial Council - Elected Mr. Asuramana Pejjalage Keerthirathne and Mr. N. T. M. M. Thahir of United People's Freedom Alliance as Members of North Western Provincial Council
